  "texts": [
    "We consider this kind of implicit information learnable and therefore do not exclude them from ORD records.",
    "On the other hand, some implicit information is considered unlearnable and thus excluded from the ORD records.",
    "Specifically,",
    "• Unspecified outcome: If the name of a product is present in the ORD record and is not explicitly stated in the reaction text, this name is removed from the ORD record.",
    "This could happen when the product name is defined only in the title of the corresponding patent and not mentioned explicitly in the procedure text."
  ],
